hadiths[156]{hadithnumber,text}:
809,"Unhoney Amr bin Saeed padhi. sey. jab wo Makka ki taraf (Abdullah bin Zuber sey qitaal key liye) lashkar rawana kar rahey they kaha : aey Ameer ! mujhey ijazat dijiye ki main aap sey eik aisi baat bayan karun jisey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fateh Makka key doosrey din farmaya, merey kanon ney isey suna , merey dil ney isey yad rakha aur meri aakhon ney aap ko dekha , jab aap ney ye hadees bayan farmaee to Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki phir farmaya : ''Makka (mein jang aur jidaal karna) Allah ney haram kiya hai. logon ney haram nahin kiya hai, lihaza kisi shakhs key liye jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, ye jayez nahin ke wo is mein khoon bahaaey , ya uska koi darkht kaatey. agar koi is mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qitaal ko daleel bana kar (qitaal ka ( jayaz hona nikaley to us sey kaho : Allah ney apney Rasool Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko uski ijazat di thi, tumhen nahin di hai. to mujhey bhi din key kuchh waqt key liye aaj ijazat thi, aaj iski hurmat wesey hi lot aai hai jaisey kal thi. jo log mojud hain wo ye baat un logon ko pahuncha den jo mojud nahin hain.''  Abu-Shuraih sey puchha gaya : is par Amr bin Saeed ney aap sey kya kaha? kaha : usney mujh sey kaha : Abu-Shuraih ! main ye baat aap sey ziyada achchhi tarah janta hun, Haram Makka kisi nafarman (yani baaghi) ko panah nahin deta aur na kisi ka khoon kar key bhagney waley ko aur na chori kar key bhagney waley ko. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Shuraih (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu-Shuraih Khuzai ka naam Khuwelid bin Amr hai. aur yehi adwi aur ka'bi yehi hain. 3- is bab mein Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4-  (ولا فارا بخربة) ki bajaey  (ولا فارا بخزية)  aur yaa key sath bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 5- aur « wala فارا بخربة » mein « خربہ » key maana gunah aur jurm key hain yani jisney koi jurm kiya ya khoon kya phir Haram mein panah li to is par had jari ki jaeygi."
810,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Haj aur Umra eik key baad doosrey ko ada karo isliye ke ye dono faqr (gharibi) aur gunahon ko is tarah mita detey hain jaisey bhatti lohey, soney aur chaandi key mail ko mita deti hai aur Haj mabroor padhi. ka badla sirf jannat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood ki hadees Hasan hai, aur ibne-Masood ki riwayat sey gharib hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Aamir bin Rabeea , Abu-Hurera , Abdullah bin Habshi , Umme-Salma aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
811,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney haj kiya aur usney koi fohsh aur behudaa baat nahin ki, aur na hi koi gunah ka kaam kiya padhi. to uskey guzishta (pichhle) tamam gunah padhi. bakhsh diye jaeyngey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai."
812,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''safar ka kharch aur sawari ka Malik ho jo usey Baitullah tak pahuncha sakey aur wo Haj na karey to is mein koi farq nahin ke wo Yahudi ho kar marey ya Esai ho kar, aur ye isliye ke Allah ney apni kitab (Quran) mein farmaya hai : ''Allah key liye Baitullah ka Haj karna logon par farz hai jo us tak pahunchney ki istataat rakhtey hon.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- iski sanad mein kalam hai. Hilal bin Abdullah majhool (anjaan) Raavi hain. aur Haris hadees mein zaeef gardaaney jatey hain."
813,"Eik shakhs ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya chiz Haj wajib karti hai? aap ney farmaya : ''safar, kharch aur sawari.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Ibrahim hi ibne Yazeed Khoozi Makki hain aur inke hafizey ke talluq sey baaz ehle-ilm ney un par kalaam kiya hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aadmi jab safar, kharch aur sawari ka Malik ho jaey to is par Haj wajib ho jata hai."
814,"Jab ye hukm nazil huwa ke ''Allah key liye logon par Khana-Kaaba ka Haj farz hai jo us tak pahunchney ki taqat rakhen.''  to logon ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya Haj har saal (farz hai)? aap khamosh rahey. logon ney phir puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya har saal? aap ney farmaya : ''nahi'', aur  agar main haan keh deta to (har saal) wajib ho jata aur phir Allah ney ye hukm nazil farmaya : ''aey eman walo ! aisi chizon key barey mein mat puchha karo ke agar wo tumharey liye zahir kar di jaeyn to tum par shaaq (bura) guzren.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- Abul-Bakhtari ka naam Saeed bin Abi Imran hai aur yehi Saeed bin Firoz hain. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
815,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney teen Haj kiye, do Haj hijrat sey pehley aur eik Haj hijrat key baad, uskey sath aap ney Umra bhi kya aur tirsatdh oont hadi key taur par sath ley gaey aur baaqi oont Yamen sey Ali ley kar aaye. un mein Abu-Jahal ka eik oont tha. uski naak mein chaandi ka eik halqa tha. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen nahar (qurban) kiya, phir aap ney har oont mein sey eik eik tukda ley kar usey pakaaney ka hukm diya, to pakaya gaya aur aap ney uska shorbaa piya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Sufiyan ki riwayat sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf Zaid bin Hubaab key tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Abdullah bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi ko dekha ke unhoney apni kitabon mein ye hadees Abdullah bin abi Ziyad key wastey sey riwayat ki hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key silsiley mein puchha to wo isey ba-riwayat (Sauri an Jaafar an Abeeh an Jabir an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) nahin jaan sakey, mainey unhen dekha ke unhoney is hadees ko mehfooz shumar nahin kiya, aur kaha : ye Sauri sey riwayat ki jati hai aur Sauri ney Abu-Is'haq sey aur Abu-Is'haq ney Mujahid sey mursalan riwayat ki hai."
816,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chaar Umerey kiye : Hudebiya ka Umrah, doosra Umra agley saal yani zi-qaada mein qaza ka umrah, teesra Umra Jaarana padhi. ka, chotha Umra jo apney Haj key sath kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Anas , Abdullah bin Amr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
817,"jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Haj ka irada kiya to aap ney logon mein aelan karaya. (Madina mein) log ikhatta ho gaey, chunanche jab aap (wahan sey chal kar) bedaa pahunchey to ehraam baandha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Anas , Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
818,Bedaa jis key barey mein log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par jhoot baandhtey hain (ke wahan sey ehraam baandha) padhi. Allah ki qism ! Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney masjid (zul-hulefa) key paas darkht key qarib talbiya pukara. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
819,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney namaz key baad ehraam baandha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum Abdus-Salaam bin Harab key ilawa kisi ko nahin jantey jisney ye hadees riwayat ki ho 3- jis chiz ko ehle-ilm ney mustahab qarar diya hai wo yehi hai ke aadmi namaz key baad ehraam baandhey.
820,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajje-afrad padhi. kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajje-afrad kiya, Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) ney bhi afrad kiya. 5- Sauri kehtey hain ke Hajje-afrad karo to bhi behtar hai, Hajje-Quran karo to bhi behtar hai aur Hajje-tamattoa' karo to bhi behtar hai. Shafai ney bhi isi jaisi baat kahi. 6- kaha : hamein sab sey ziyada afrad pasand hai phir tamatto aur phir Quran."
821,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko « لبيك بعمرة وحجة » farmatey suna. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr aur Imran bin Husain sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, ehle-Koofa waghera ney isi ko ikhtiyar kiya hai."
822,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajje-tamattoa' kiya padhi. aur Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) ney bhi padhi. aur sab sey pehley jisney us sey roka wo Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
823,"Unhoney Saad bin Abi Waqas aur Zuhaak bin Qais Raziallahu anhuma sey suna , dono Umra ko Haj mein milaaney ka zikr kar rahey they. Zuhaak bin Qais ney kaha : aisa wohi kerega jo Allah key hukm sey na-waqif ho, is par Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : bahut buri baat hai jo tum ney kahi , merey bhatijey ! to Zuhaak bin Qais ney kaha : umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney is sey mana kiya hai, is par Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey kiya hai aur aap key sath hamney bhi isey kiya hai.  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
824,"Salim bin Abdullah ney un sey bayan kiya ke unhoney ehale-shaam mein sey eik shakhs sey suna , wo Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey Haj mein Umra sey faeyda uthaney key barey mein poochh raha tha, to Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : ye jayez hai. is par Shaami ney kaha : aap key walid ney to is sey roka hai? Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ney kaha : zara tum hi bataao agar merey walid kisi chiz sey roken aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey kiya ho to merey walid key hukm ki perwi ki jaeygi ya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key hukm ki, to usney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key hukm ki, to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aisa kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees (822) Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Usman , Jabir , Saad , Asma binte Abi Bakr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey eik jamaat ney isi ko pasand kiya hai ke Haj mein Umra ko shamil kar key Hajje-tamattoa' karna durust hai. 4- aur Hajje-tamattoa' ye hai ke aadmi Haj key mahinon mein Umerey key zariey dakhil ho, phir Umra kar key wahin thehra rahey yahan tak ke Haj kar ley to wo mutmattea' (fayeda uthaana) hai, is par hadi ki jo usey muyassar ho, qurbani lazim hogi , agar usey hadi na mil sakey to Haj mein teen din aur ghar lot kar saat din key rozey rakhey.  5- mutmattea' (fayeda uthaana) key liye mustahab hai ke jab wo Haj mein teen rozey rakhey to zil-hijja key (ibtidaai) das dino mein rakhey aur uska aakhiri roza Arfa ke din ka ho, aur Sahaba kiram mein sey baaz ehle-ilm jin mein ibne-Umar aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain key qol ki taraf sey agar wo das dino mein ye rozey na rakh sakey to tashreeq ke dino mein rakh ley. yehi Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 6- aur baaz kehtey hain : tashreeq ke dino mein roza nahin rakheyga.  ye ehle-koofa ka qol hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ehale-hadees Haj mein Umerey ko shamil kar key Hajje-tamattoa' karney ko pasand kartey hain, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
825,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka talbiya ye tha :(لبيك اللهم لبيك لبيك لا شريك لك لبيك إن الحمد والنعمة لك والملك لا شريك لك) ''hazir hun, aey Allah main hazir hun, hazir hun, tera koi shareek nahin main hazir hun.  sab tareef aur nemat teri hi hai aur saltanat bhi, tera koi shareek nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Jabir , Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) , ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Sufiyan , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 4- Shafai kehtey hain : agar wo Allah ki tazeem key kuchh kalimaat ka izafa kar ley to koi harj nahin hoga. Insha-Allah. lekin merey nazdik pasandida baat ye hai ke wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key talbiya par iktifa karey (kaafi samjhey). Shafai kehtey hain : hamney jo ye kaha ke ''Allah ki tazeem (izzat) key kuchh kalimaat badha leney mein koi harj nahin to is daleel sey ke ibne-Umar sey marvi (rwayat hui ( hai ke unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey talbiya yad kiya phir apni taraf sey us mein (لبيك والرغباء إليك والعمل) ''hazir hun, teri hi taraf raghbat hai aur amal bhi terey hi liye hai'' ka izafa kiya."
826,"Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma kehtey they : ye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka talbiya hai, phir wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key talbiya key akheer main apni taraf sey in alfaz ka izafa kartey : (لبيك لبيك وسعديك والخير في يديك لبيك والرغباء إليك والعمل) ''hazir hun teri khidmat mein hazir hun teri khidmat mein aur khush hun teri tabedari par aur har tarah ki bhalai terey hi dono haathon mein hai aur teri taraf raghbat hai aur amal bhi terey hi liye hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
827,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha gaya ke kon sa Haj afzal hai? aap ney farmaya : ''jis mein kasrat sey talbiya pukara gaya ho aur khub khoon bahaayaa gaya ho.''
828,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo musalman bhi talbiya pukarta hai uskey daain ya baain paey janey waley pathar , darkht aur dheley sabhi talbiya pukartey hain, yahan tak ke dono taraf ki zamin key aakhiri sirey tak ki cheezen sabhi talbiya pukaarti hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai, hum isey ibne-Abi Fidya hi key tareeq sey jantey hain, unhoney Zuhaak bin Usman sey riwayat ki hai. 2- Muhammad bin Munkadir ney Abdur-Rehman bin Yarboo' sey isey nahin suna hai, albatta Muhammad bin Munkadir ney basanad :(Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Yarboo' an Abiy Abdur-Rehman bin Yarboo') is hadees key ilawa dusri cheezen riwayat ki hain. 3- Abu Nuaim Taahaan Zaraar bin Surad ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (ابن أبي فديك an الضحاك بن عثمان an محمد بن المنكدر an سعيد بن عبدالرحمٰن بن يربوع an أبيه an أبي بكر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) riwayat ki hai aur is mein Zaraar sey ghalati hui hai. 4- Ahmed bin Hanbal kehtey hain : jisney is hadees mein yun kaha : (an Muhammad bin Munkadir an ibne Abdur-Rehman bin Yarboo' an Abeeh) usney ghalati ki hai. 5- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey Zaraar bin Surad ki hadees zikr ki jisey unhoney ibne-Abi Fidya sey riwayat ki hai to unhoney kaha : ye ghalat hai, mainey kaha : isey doosrey logon ney bhi unhin ki tarah ibne-Abi Fidya sey riwayat ki hai to unhoney kaha : ye kuch nahin hai logon ney isey ibne-Abi Fidya sey riwayat kiya hai aur is mein Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai, mainey Bukhari ko dekha ke wo Zaraar bin Surad ko zaeef thehra rahey they. 6- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 7- (عج) : talbiya mein aawaz buland karney ko aur (ثج) : oontniyaan nahar ( zibeh ( karney ko kehtey hain."
829,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' merey paas Jibreel ney aa kar mujhey hukm diya ke main apney Sahaba ko hukm dun ke wo talbiya main apni aawaz buland karen.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Khallad bin Sayib ki hadees jisey unhoney apney walid sey riwayat ki hai, Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees b-tareeq : (Khallad bin Sayib an Ziad bin Khalid an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, lekin ye sahih nahin hai. sahih yehi hai ke Khallad bin Sayib ney apney baap sey riwayat ki hai, aur ye Khallad bin Sayib bin Khallad bin Suwed Ansari hain. 3- is bab mein Zaid bin Khalid , Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
830,Unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap ney ehraam baandhney key liye apney kapdey utarey aur ghusl kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney ehraam baandhney key waqt ghusl karney ko mustahab qarar diya hai. yehi Shafai bhi kehtey hain.
831,"Eik shakhs ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum ehraam kahan sey baandhen? aap ney farmaya : ''ehale-Madina zul-hulefa sey ehraam baandhen, ehal Sham Johfa padhi. sey aur ehale-Najad qarn sey. aur logon ka kehna hai ke ehale-Yamen yalamlam sey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Jabir bin Abdullah aur Abdullah bin umr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
832,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ehale mashriq ki meeqaat aqeeq padhi. muqarrar ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Muhammad bin Ali hi abu Jaafar Muhammad bin Ali bin Husain bin Ali ibne-Abi Talib hain.
833,"Eik shakhs ney khadey ho kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! aap hamein ehraam mein kon kon sey kapdey pehanney ka hukm detey hain? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''na qamis pahno, na paajaama, na amaamey aur na mozey, siwaaye iske ke kisi key paas jootey na hon to wo khuf (chamdey key mozey) pehney aur usey kaat kar takhne sey nichey kar ley padhi. aur na aisa koi kapda pahno jis mein za'fraan ya waras laga ho, aur mohrim aurat naqab na lagaaey aur na dastaane pehney.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm isi par amal hai."
834,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) ko jab tehband muyassar na ho to paajaama pehan ley aur jab jootey muyassar na hon to (khuf) (chamdey key mozey) pehan ley.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) teh band na paey to paajaama pehan ley, aur jab jootey na paey to (khuf) (chamdey key mozey) pehan ley. ye Ahmed ka qol hai. 4- baaz ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki buniyad par jisey unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai kaha hai ke jab wo jootey na paey to (khuf) (chamdey ke mozey) pehney aur usey kaat kar takhne key nichey kar ley, Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , aur Malik isi key qaail hain."
835,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik Erabi (dehati) (dehaati) ko dekha jo ehraam ki haalat mein kurta pehney huye tha. to aap ney isey hukm diya ke wo isey utaar dey.
836,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi mafhoom ki hadees riwayat kartey hain. ye ziyada sahih hai aur hadees main eik qissa hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : isi tarah isey Qatada , Hujjaaj bin Irtaat aur doosrey kaee logon ney Ata sey aur unhoney Yala bin Umayya sey riwayat ki hai. lekin sahih wohi hai jisey Amr bin Dinar aur ibne-Jurej ney Ata sey , aur Ata ney Safwan bin Yala sey aur Safwan ney apney walid Yala sey aur Yala ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
837,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''paanch moozi janwer hain jo Haram mein ya haalate ehraam mein bhi maarey ja saktey hain : chuhiyaa , bichchhu , kawwa , cheel , kaat khaney wala kutta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera , abu-Saeed aur ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
838,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) sarkash darindey , kaat khaney waley kuttey , choohaa , bichchhu , cheel aur kowey maar sakta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo kehtey hain : mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) zulm dhaney waley darindon ko maar sakta hai, Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka bhi yehi qol hai. Shafai kehtey hain : mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) har us darindey ko jo logon ko ya janweron ko nuksaan pahunchaaey, maar sakta hai."
839,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pachhna lagwaayaa aur aap mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas padhi. , Abdullah bin Buhena padhi. aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) ko pachhna lagwaaney ki ijazat di hai. wo kehtey hain ke wo baal nahin mundaaeyga. 4- Malik kehtey hain ke mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) pachhnaa nahin lagwa sakta, siwaye iske ke zaruri ho. 5- Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai kehtey hain : mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) key pachhna lagwaaney mein koi harj nahin lekin wo baal nahin utaar sakta."
840,"Ibne Maamar ney apney betey ki shaadi karni chahi, to unhoney mujhey Aban bin Usman key paas bheja , wo Makka mein Ameere-Haj they. main unkey paas aaya aur mainey un sey kaha : aap key bhai apney betey ki shaadi karna chahtey hain aur chahtey hain ke aap ko is par gawah banaeyn, to unhoney kaha : main unhen eik ganwaar Erabi (dehati) (dehati) samajhta hun, mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) na khud nikah kar sakta aur na kisi ka nikah kara sakta hai. (أو كما قال) phir unhoney (apney walid) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat kartey huye isi key tarah bayan kiya, wo isey marfoo riwayat kar rahey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Raafey aur Memuna (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz Sahaba kiram jin mein umr bin Khattab , Ali bin Abi Talib aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) bhi shamil hain isi par amal hai, aur yehi baaz Tabe-een fuqaha ka bhi qol hai aur Malik , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi yehi kehtey hain. ye log mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) key liye nikah karna jayez nahin samajhtey, in logon ka kehna hai ke agar mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) ney nikah kar liya to uska nikah batil hoga."
841,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey nikah kiya aur aap halal they phir unki khilwat (tanhaai) mein gaey tab bhi aap halal they, aur main hi aap dono key darmiyan pegham pahuchaane-wala tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- aur hum Hammad bin Zaid key ilawa kisi aisey shakhs ko nahin jantey jisney isey Matar Warraq key wastey sey Rabeea sey musnadan riwayat kiya ho. 3- aur Malik bin Anas ney Rabeea sey , aur Rabeea ney Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Yasar sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey shaadi ki aur aap halal they. isey Malik ney mursalan riwayat kiya hai, aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Hilal ney bhi isey Rabeea sey mursalan riwayat kiya hai. 4- Yazeed bin Asamm Ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat kartey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujh sey shaadi ki aur aap halal they yani mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) nahin they. Yazeed bin Asamm Memuna key bhaanjey hain."
842,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey shaadi ki aur aap mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory aur ehle-koofa bhi kehtey hain.
843,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey shaadi ki aur aap mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) they.
844,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey shaadi ki to aap mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Memuna sey shaadi karney key barey mein logon ka ikhtilaf hai. isliye ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Makkey key raastey mein un sey shaadi ki thi, baaz logon ney kaha : aap ney jab un sey shaadi ki to aap halal they albatta aap key un sey shaadi karney ki baat zahir hui to aap mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) they, aur aap ney Makkey key raastey mein maqam sarf mein unkey sath khilwat (tanhaai) mein gaey to bhi aap halal they. Memuna ka intiqal bhi sarf mein huwa jahan Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey khilwat ki thi aur wo maqame sarf main hi dafn ki gaeen."
845,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey shaadi ki aur aap halal they aur un sey khilwat ki to bhi aap halal they. aur unhoney sarf hi mein intiqal kiya, hamney unhen usi saya daar maqam mein dafn kiya jahan aap ney un sey khilwat ki thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- deegar kaee logon ney ye hadees Yazeed bin Asamm sey mursalan riwayat ki hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Memuna sey shaadi ki aur aap halal they."
846,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khushki ka shikar tumharey liye haalate ehraam mein halal hai jabke tum ney uska shikar khud na kiya ho, na hi wo tumharey liye kiya gaya ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abu-Qatada aur Talha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- Jabir ki hadees mufassar hai. 3- aur hum Muttalib ka Jabir sey sun'na, nahin jantey. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) key liye shikar key khaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey jab usney khud uska shikar na kiya ho, na hi wo uskey liye kiya gaya ho. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : ye is baab mein marvi (riwayat hui) sab sey achchhi aur qiyas key sab sey ziyada muwaafiq hadees hai, aur isi par amal hai. aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
847,"wo Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, yahan tak ke aap jab Makkey ka kuchh raasta tey kar chukey to wo apney baaz mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) sathiyon key sath peechhey reh gaey jabke Abu-Qatada khud ghair-mohrim they, isi doran unhoney eik neel gaey dekha, to wo apney ghodey par sawar huye aur apney sathiyon sey darkhaast ki ke wo unhen unka kudra (kodaa) utha kar dey den to un logon ney isey unhen deney sey inkar kiya. phir unhoney un sey apna neza manga  to un logon ney isey bhi utha kar deney sey inkar kiya to unhoney usey khud hi (utar kar) utha liya aur shikar ka peechha kiya aur usey maar dala , to baaz Sahaba kiram ney us shikar mein sey khaya aur baaz ney nahin khaya. phir wo Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey aa kar miley aur is barey mein aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''ye to eik aisi ghiza hai jisey Allah ney tumhen khilaya hai.''"
848,Abu-Qatada sey neel gaey key barey mein abu-Nazar hi ki hadees ki tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai albatta Zaid bin Aslam ki is hadees mein itna zayed hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas uskey gosht mein sey kuchh hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
849,"Sa'ab bin Jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhen bataya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam abwa ya wadan mein unke paas sey guzrey, to unhoney aap ko eik neel gaey hadiya kiya, to aap ney isey lota diya. unke chehrey par nagawari key aasaar zahir huye, jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey dekha to farmaya : ''hum tumhen lauta'te nahin lekin hum mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat isi hadees ki taraf gaee hai aur unhoney mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) key liye shikar ka gosht khaney ko makrooh kaha hai. 3- Shafai kehtey hain : hamarey nazdik is hadees ki tauzeeh ye hai ke aap ney wo gosht sirf isliye lota diya ke aap ko guman huwa ke wo aap hi ki khatir shikar kiya gaya hai. so aap ney isey khahish ke taur par chhod diya . 4- Zohri key baaz shagirdon ney ye hadees Zohri sey riwayat ki hai. aur is mein « أهدى له حمارا وحشياً » key bajaey «أهدى له لحم حمارٍ وحشٍ» hai lekin ye ghair mehfooz hai. 5- is bab mein Ali aur Zaid bin Arqam sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
850,"Hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj ya Umerey key liye nikley they ke hamarey samney tiddi ka eik dal aa gaya, hum unhen apney kodon aur lathiyon sey maarney lagey to Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''isey khaao, kyonkey ye samandar ka shikar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Abu Muhazzim ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey unhoney Abu-Hurera sey riwayat ki hai. 2- Abu Muhazzim ka naam Yazeed bin Sufiyan hai. Shoba ney un mein kalam kiya hai. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney mohrim (aehram ki haalat mein shakhs) ko tiddi ka shikar karney aur usey khaney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai. 4- aur baaz ka khayal hai ke agar wo uska shikar karey aur usey khaye to is par fidya hai."
851,"Mainey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya lakad-baggha shikar mein dakhil hai? unhoney kaha : haan, (phir) mainey puchha : kya main usey kha sakta hun? unhoney kaha : haan , mainey kaha : kya isey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai? unhoney kaha : haan. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2 - Ali bin Madeeni kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed ka bayan hai ke ye hadees Jareer bin Hazam ney bhi riwayat ki hai lekin unhoney Jabir sey aur Jabir ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki hai, ibne-Jurej ki hadees ziyada sahih hai. 3- aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. aur baaz ehle-ilm ka amal isi hadees par hai ke mohrim jab lagad- bagghe ka shikar karey ya usey khaye to is par fidya hai."
852,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Makkey mein dakhil honey key liye fakh (maqam) mein padhi. ghusl kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ghair mehfooz hai. 2- sahih wo riwayat hai jisey Nafey ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai ke wo Makkey mein dakhil honey key liye ghusl kartey they. aur yehi Shafai bhi kehtey hain ke Makkey mein dakhil honey key liye ghusl karna mustahab hai. 3- Abdur-Rehman bin Zaid bin Aslam hadees mein zaeef hain. Ahmed bin Hanbal aur Ali bin Madeeni wagaira ney in ko zaeef thehraaya hai aur hum is hadees ko sirf unhi key tareeq sey marfoo jantey hain.
853,"Jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka aatey to bulandi ki taraf sey dakhil hotey aur nasheb (dhaal) ki taraf sey nikaltey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai,"
854,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein din key waqt dakhil huye they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
855,"Jabir bin Abdullah sey puchha gaya : jab aadmi Baitullah ko dekhey to kya apney dono haath uthaey? unhoney kaha : hamney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kiya, to kya hum aisa kartey they?  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Baitullah ko dekh kar haath uthaney ki hadees hum Shoba hi key tareeq sey jantey hain, Shoba Abu Qaza' sey riwayat kartey hain, aur Abu Qaza' ka naam Suwed bin Hujair hai."
856,"Jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka aaye to aap Masjide-Haram mein dakhil huye, aur Hajare-Aswad ka bosa liya , phir apney daain janib chaley aap ney teen chakkar mein ramal kiya padhi. aur chaar chakkar mein aam chaal chaley. phir aap ney maqame-Ibrahim key paas aa kar farmaya : ''maqame Ibrahim ko namaz padhney ki jagah banao.'' , chunanche aap ney do rakat namaz padhi , aur maqame-Ibrahim aap key aur Baitullah key darmiyan tha. phir do rakat key baad Hajare-Aswad key paas aa kar uska istilaam kiya. phir Safa ki taraf gaey. mera khayal hai ke (wahan) aap ney ye aayat padhi : (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله) ''safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadees aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
857,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajare-Aswad sey Hajare-Aswad tak teen pheron mein ramal padhi. kiya aur chaar mein aam chal chaley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- Shafai kehtey hain : jab koi jaan boojh kar ramal karna chhod dey to usney ghalat kiya lekin is par koi chiz wajib nahin aur jab usney ibtidaai teen pheron mein ramal na kiya ho to baqi mein nahin karega. 5- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : ehale Makka key liye ramal nahin hai aur na hi is par jisney Makka sey ehraam baandha ho."
858,"Main ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma key sath tha, Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) jis rukn key bhi paas sey guzartey , uska istilaam kartey padhi. to ibne-Abbas ney un sey kaha : Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajare-Aswad aur rukn yamaani key ilawa kisi ka istilaam nahin kiya, is par Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : Baitullah ki koi chiz chhodi janey key laaiq nahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai,.  2- is bab mein umr sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Hajare-Aswad aur rukn yamaani key ilawa kisi ka istilaam na kiya jaey."
859,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam neyiztibaa ki haalat mein Baitullah ka tawaf kiya, aap key jism Mubarak par eik chadar thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- yehi Sauri ki hadees hai jisey unhoney ibne-Jurej sey riwayat ki hai aur isey hum Sirf key inhi tareeq sey jantey hain. 3- Abdul-Hameed Jubera bin Sheba key betey hain. jinhoney ibne Yala sey aur ibne Yala ney apney walid sey riwayat ki hai aur Yala sey murad Yala bin Umayya hain (Raziallahu anhu)."
860,"Mainey umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hajare-Aswad ka bosa letey dekha , wo keh rahey they : main tera bosa ley raha hun aur mujhey malum hai ke to eik patthar hai, agar mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko tera bosa letey na dekha hota to main tujhey bosa na leta. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakar aur ibne-Umar sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
861,"Eik shakhs ney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey Hajare-Aswad ka bosa leney key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko usey chhotey aur bosa letey dekha hai. usney kaha : achchha bataiye agar main wahan tak pahunchney mein maghloob ho (haar) jaaun aur agar main bheed mein phans jaaun? to is par ibne-Umar ney kaha : tum (ye apna) agar-magar Yamen mein rakho padhi. mainey Aabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko usey chhotey aur bosa letey dekha hai. ye Zuber bin Arbi wohi hain, jin sey Hammad bin Zaid ney riwayat ki hai, Kufey key rehney waley they, un ki kunniyat Abu-Salma hai. unhoney Anas bin Malik aur doosrey kaee Sahaba sey hadisein riwayat kin hain. aur un sey Sufiyan Sory aur doosrey kaee aur Aaimma ney riwayat ki hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. un sey ye dusri sanadon sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo Hajare-Aswad key bosa leney ko mustahab samajhtey hain. agar ye mumkin na ho aur aadmi wahan tak na pahunch sakey to usey apney haath sey chu ley aur apney haath ka bosa ley ley aur agar wo us tak na pahunch sakey to jab uskey samney mein pahunchey to uski taraf rukh karey aur Allahu-Akbar kahey , ye Shafai ka qol hai."
862,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jis waqt Makka aaye to aap ney Baitullah key saat chakkar lagaey aur ye aayat padhi : (‏‏‏‏ واتخذوا من مقام إبراهيم مصلى) ''maqame-Ibrahim ko namazi banao yani wahan namaz padho'' (Al-Baqra :125), phir maqame-Ibrahim key peechhey namaz padhi, phir Hajare-Aswad key paas aaye aur uska istilaam kiya phir farmaya : ''hum (saee) isi sey shuru karen gey jis sey Allah ney shuru kiya hai. chunanche aap ney Safa sey saee shuru ki aur ye aayat padhi : (إن الصفا والمروة من شعائر الله) ''safa aur Marwa Allah ki nishaniyon mein sey hain'' (Al-Baqra :158). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- usi par ehle-ilm ka amal hai ke saee Marwa key bajaey Safa sey shuru ki jaey. agar kisi ney Safa key bajaey Marwa sey saee shuru kar di to ye saee kafi na hogi aur saee phir sey Safa sey shuru karega. 3- ehle-ilm ka is shakhs key barey mein ikhtilaf hai ke jisney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee nahin ki, yahan tak ke wapis ghar chala gaya, baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke agar kisi ney Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee nahin ki yahan tak ke wo Makka sey bahar nikal aaya phir usey yad aaya , aur wo Makkey key qarib hai to wapis ja kar Safa aur Marwa ki saee karey. aur agar usey yad nahin aaya yahan tak ke wo apney mulk wapis aa gaya to usey kafi ho jaeyga lekin is par dam lazim hoga, yehi Sufiyan Sory ka qol hai. aur baaz kehtey hain ke agar usney Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee chhod di yahan tak ke apney mulk wapis aa gaya to ye usey kafi na hoga. ye Shafai ka qol hai, wo kehtey hain ke Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee wajib hai, uskey baghair Haj durust nahin."
863,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee ki, taake mushrekin ko apni quwat dikha saken. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm isi ko mustahab samajhtey hain ke aadmi Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan saee karey, agar wo saee na karey balke Safa aur Marwa key darmiyan aam chaal chaley to usey jayez samajhtey hain."
864,"Mainey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ko saee mein aam chaal chaltey dekha to mainey un sey kaha : kya aap Safa aur Marwa ki saee mein aam chaal chaltey hain? unhoney kaha : agar main daudun to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko daudtey bhi dekha hai, aur agar main aam chaal chalun to mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aam chaal chaltey bhi dekha hai, aur main kafi boodha hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Saeed bin Juber key wastey sey ibne-Umar sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
865,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apni sawari par Baitullah ka tawaf kiya jab padhi. aap Hajare-Aaswad key paas pahunchtey to uski taraf ishara kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , abu-Tufel aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney Baitullah ka tawaf , aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee sawar ho kar karney ko makrooh kaha hai siwaye iske  ke koi uzr ho, yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
866,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Baitullah ka tawaf pachas baar kiya to wo apney gunahon sey is tarah nikal aayega jaisey isi din uski maa ney isey janm diya hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Anas aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 2- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : ye to ibne-Abbas sey unke apney qol sey riwayat kiya jata hai.
867,log Abdullah bin Saeed bin Juber ko unkey walid sey afzal shumar kartey they. aur Abdullah ke eik bhai hain jinhen Abdul-Malik bin Saeed bin Juber kehtey hain. unhoney un sey bhi riwayat ki hai.
868,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''aey Bani Abd Munaaf ! raat din key kisi bhi hissey mein kisi ko is ghar ka tawaf karney aur namaz padhney sey na roko.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Juber Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abdullah bin Abi Najeeh ney bhi ye hadees Abdullah bin Babaah sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Abu-Zar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- makkey mein Asr key baad aur Fajr key baad namaz padhney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain : Asr key baad aur Fajr key baad namaz padhney aur tawaf karney mein koi harj nahin hai. ye Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai padhi. unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees padhi. sey daleel li hai. aur baaz kehtey hain : agar koi Asr key baad tawaf karey to suraj doobney tak namaz na padhey. isi tarah agar koi Fajr key baad tawaf karey to suraj nikalney tak namaz na padhey. un ki daleel umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees hai ke unhoney Fajr key baad tawaf kiya aur namaz nahin padhi phir Makka sey nikal gaey yahan tak ke wo zi-tuwa mein utrey to suraj nikal janey key baad namaz padhi. ye Sufiyan Sory aur Malik bin Anas ka qol hai."
869,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tawaf ki do rakat mein ikhlas ki dono suraten yani «قل يا أيها الكافرون » aur « قل هو الله أحد » padhin.
870,wo tawaf ki dono rakaaton mein : « قل يا أيها الكافرون » aur « قل هو الله أحد » padhney ko mustahab samajhtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Sufiyan ki Jaafar bin Muhammad an Abiy ki riwayat Abdul-Azeez bin Imran ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 2- aur (Sufiyan ki riwayat karda) Jaafar bin Muhammad ki hadees jisey wo apney walid (key amal) sey riwayat kartey hain (Abdul-Azeez ki riwayat karda) Jaafar bin Muhammad ki is hadees sey ziyada sahih hai jisey wo apney walid sey aur wo Jabir sey aur wo Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- Abdul-Azeez bin Imran hadees mein zaeef hain.
871,"Mainey Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : aap ko kin baaton ka hukm dey kar bheja gaya hai? padhi. unhoney kaha : chaar baaton ka : jannat mein sirf wohi jaan dakhil hogi jo musalman ho, Baitullah ka tawaf koi nanga ho kar na karey. musalman aur mushrik us saal key baad jama na hon, jis kisi ka Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey koi ehad ho to uska ye ehad uski muddat tak key liye hoga. aur jiski koi muddat na ho to uski muddat chaar maah hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
872,"Hum sey Sufiyan bin Uena ney bayan kiya aur Sufiyan ney Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki, albatta ibne-Abi umr aur Nasar bin Ali ney (Zaid bin Asaie key bajaey) Zaid bin Yasee' kaha hai, aur ye ziyada sahih hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Shoba ko is mein weham huwa hai, unhoney : Zaid bin Usail kaha hai."
873,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey paas sey nikal kar gaey, aap ki aankhen thandi thin aur tabiat khush , phir merey paas laut kar aaye, to ghamgin aur dukhi they, mainey aap sey (wajeh) poochhi, to aap ney farmaya : ''main Kaabe key andar gaya. aur meri khahish hui ke kaash! mainey aisa na kiya hota. main dar raha hun ke apney baad mainey apni ummat ko zehmat mein dal diya.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
874,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Kaabe key andar namaz padhi. jabke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain : aap ney namaz nahin padhi balke aap ney sirf takbir kahi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Usama bin Zaid, Fazal bin Abbas , Usman bin Talha aur Sheeba bin Usman (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo Kaabe key andar namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey. 4- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain : Kaabe mein nafl namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin, aur unhoney Kaabe ke andar farz namaz padhney ko makrooh kaha hai. 5- Shafai kehtey hain : Kaabe ke andar farz aur nafl koi bhi namaz padhney mein koi harj nahin isliye ke nafl aur farz ka hukm wuzu aur qibley ke barey main eik hi hai."
875,"Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma ney un sey kaha : tum mujh sey wo baaten bayan karo, jisey Ummul-momenin yani Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) tum sey raazdarana taur sey bayan kiya karti thin, unhoney kaha : mujh sey unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''agar tumhari qom ke log jahiliyat chhod kar naey naey musalman na huye hotey, to main Kaabe ko gira deta aur is mein do darwazey kar deta.''  chunanche ibne Zuber Raziallahu anhuma jab iqtidar mein aaye to unhoney Kaba gira kar is mein do darwazey kar diye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
876,"Main chahti thi ke Baitullah main dakhil ho kar is mein namaz padhun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mera haath pakda aur mujhey hateem padhi. key andar kar diya aur farmaya : ''agar tum Baitullah key andar dakhil hona chahti ho to hateem mein namaz padh lo, ye bhi Baitullah ka eik hissa hai, lekin tumhari qom key logon ney Kaabe ki taamir ke waqt isey chhota kar diya, aur itney hissey ko Baitullah sey khaarij kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
877,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Hajare-Aswad jannat sey utra, wo doodh sey ziyada safed tha, lekin usey bani Adam ke gunahon ney kaala kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin umr aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
878,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''Hajare-Aswad aur maqame-Ibrahim dono jannat ke yaqut mein sey do yaqut hain, Allah ney inka Noor khatam kar diya, agar Allah inka Noor khatam na karta to wo mashriq aur maghrib ke sarey maqam ko roshan kar detey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- ye Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas Raziallahu anhuma sey moqufan unka qol riwayat kiya jata hai. 3- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
879,"Hamein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Meena mein Zohar , Asr , Maghrib , Isha aur Fajr padhaai padhi. phir aap subah padhi. hi Arafat key liye rawana ho gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Ismail bin Muslim par un ke haafze ke talluq sey logon ney kalam kiya hai."
880,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Meena mein Zohar aur Fajr padhi, phir aap subah hi subah Arafat key liye rawana ho gaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Muqsim ki hadees ibne-Abbas sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- Shoba ka bayan hai ke Hakam ney Muqsim sey sirf paanch cheezen suni hain, aur unhoney unhen shumar kiya to ye hadees Shoba ki shumar ki hui hadeeson mein nahin thi. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Zuber aur Anas sey bhi hadeesen aai hai."
881,"hamney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! kya hum aap key liye Meena main eik ghar na bana den jo aap ko saya dey. aap ney farmaya : ''nahin padhi. , Mina mein uska haq hai jo wahan pehley pahunchey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
882,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Mina mein do rakat namaz padhi jabke log hamesha sey ziyada maamoon aur be-khof they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Harisa bin Wahab ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , ibne-Umar aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney kaha ke mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke sath Mina mein do rakatein padhin, phir Abu-Bakar key sath , umr key sath aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) key sath unkey ibtidaai daur khilaafat mein do rakatein padhin 4- ehale-Makka ke Mina mein namaze-qasr karney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ke darmiyan ikhtilaf hai. baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke ehale-Makka ke liye jayez nahin ke wo Mina mein namaz qasr karen, siwaye aisey shakhs ke jo Mina mein musafir ki haisiyat sey ho, ye ibne-Jurej , Sufiyan Sory , Yahya bin Saeed Qataan , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. baaz kehtey hain ke ehale-Makka key liye Mina mein namaz qasr karney mein koi harj nahin. ye Auzaai , Malik , Sufiyan bin Uena , aur Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi ka qol hai."
883,"hamarey paas Yazeed bin Mirbbaa Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) aaye , hum log mauqif (arafat) mein aisi jagah thehrey huye they jisey Amr bin Abdullah Imam sey door samajhtey they padhi. to Yazeed bin Mirbbaa ney kaha : main tumhari taraf Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka bheja huwa qaasid hun, tum log mushair par thehro kyonkey tum Ibrahim key waris ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Yazeed bin Mirbbaa Ansari ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isey hum sirf ibne Uena key tareeq sey jantey hain, aur ibne Uena Amr bin Dinar sey riwayat kartey hain. 3- ibne Mirbbaa ka naam Yazeed bin Mirbbaa Ansari hai, unki sirf yehi eik hadees jaani jati hai. 4- is bab mein Ali , Aaisha , Juber bin Mut-im , Shareed bin Suwed Saqafi (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
884,"Quraish aur unke hum mazhab log. aur ye (hims (bahadur)) kahlaatey hain. Muzdalfa mein wuqoof kartey they aur kehtey they : hum to Allah key khaadim hain. (Arafat nahin jatey), aur jo unke ilawa log they wo Arfa mein wuqoof kartey (theharte) they to Allah ney aayate-karima :« ثم أفيضوا من حيث أفاض الناس » ''aur tum bhi wahan sey lauto jahan sey log laut'tey hain.'' (Al-Baqra) nazil farmaae. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees key maana ye hain ke ehale-Makka Haram sey bahar nahin jatey they aur Arfa Haram sey bahar hai. ehale-Makka Muzdalfa hi mein wuqoof kartey (theharte) they aur kehtey they : hum Allah key abad kiye huye log hain. aur ehale-Makka key ilawa log Arafat mein wuqoof kartey they to Allah ney hukm nazil farmaya : « ثم أفيضوا من حيث أفاض الناس » ''tum bhi wahan sey lauto jahan sey log laut'tey hain.'' « teiswin » sey murad ehale Haram hain."
885,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Arafat mein qiyam kya aur farmaya : '' ye Arfa hai, yehi wuqoof ( theherney ( ki jagah hai, Arfa ( Arafat ( purey ka pura theherney ki jagah hai, phir aap jis waqt suraj doob gaya to wahan sey lotey . Usama bin Zaid ko peechey bithaya , aur aap apni aam raftaar sey chaltey huye apney haath sey ishara kar rahey they, aur log daain baain apney oonton ko maar rahey they, aap un ki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar kehtey jatey they : '' logo ! sukoon o waqar ko lazim pakdo '' , phir aap Muzdalfa aaye aur logon ko dono namazein ( maghrib aur Isha qasr kar key (eik sath padhaain , jab subh hui to aap Quzah padhi. aa kar thehrey , aur farmaya : '' ye Quzah hai aur ye bhi mauqif hai aur Muzdalfa pura ka pura mauqif hai'' , phir aap lotey yahan tak ke aap wadi mohsir padhi. pahunchey aur aap ney apni oontni ko maara to wo dodi yahan tak ke usney wadi paar kar li , phir aap ney wuqoof kya. aur Fazal bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ko) oontni par) peechey bithaya , phir aap jamara aaye aur rami ki, phir Manhar ( qurbani ki jagah ( aaye aur farmaya : '' ye Manhar hai, aur Mina pura ka pura Manhar ( qurbani karney ki jagah ( hai'' , qabila Khasam ki eik nojawan aurat ney aap sey masla puchha , usney arz kya : merey walid boodhey ho chukey hain aur un par Allah ka fariza Haj wajib ho chuka hai. kya main un ki taraf sey Haj kar lun to kafi hoga ? aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' haan , apney baap ki taraf sey Haj kar ley ''. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Fazal ki gardan mod di, is par aap sey , Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! aap ney apney chacha zaad bhai ki gardan kyon palat di ? to aap ney farmaya : ''main ney dekha ke ladka aur ladki dono jawan hain to main un dono key silsiley mein shetan sey maamoon nahin raha '' padhi. , phir eik shakhs ney aap key paas aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey sar mundaaney sey pehley tawaf ifaaza kar liya . aap ney farmaya : '' sar mundwaa lo ya baal katarwaa lo koi harj nahin hai ''. phir eik doosrey shakhs ney aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! mainey rami karney sey pehley qurbani kar li , aap ney farmaya : '' rami kar lo koi harj nahin '' 4- phir aap baitullah aaye aur uska tawaf kya, phir zamzam par aaye , aur farmaya : '' bani abdul-Muttalib ! agar ye andesha na hota ke log tumhen maghloob kar dengey to main bhi) tumharey sath (pani kheenchta''. (aur logon ko pilaatey (Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. hum usey Ali ki riwayat sey sirf usi tareeq sey jantey hain. yani Abdur-Rehman bin Haris bin Ayash ki sanad sey , aur deegar kaee logon ney bhi Sory sey usi key misl riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, unka khayal hai ke Arfa mein Zohar key waqt Zohar aur Asr ko mila kar eik sath padhey , 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : jab aadmi apney derey ( khemey ( mein namaz padhey aur Imam key sath namaz mein shareek na ho to chahey dono namazon ko eik sath jama aur qasr kar key padh ley , jaisa ke Imam ney kya hai."
886,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam wadi Mehsar mein tez chaal chaley .) Bishr ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke) aap Muzdalfa sey lotey , aap pursukoon yani aam raftaar sey chal rahey they, logon ko bhi aap ney sukoon o itminan sey chalney ka hukm diya .) aur Abu-Nuem ki riwayat mein itna izafa hai ke) aap ney unhen aisi kankariyon sey rami karney ka hukm diya jo do ungliyon mein pakdi ja saken, aur farmaya : '' shayad mein us saal key baad tumhen na dekh sakun ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Usama bin Zaid Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
887,ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney Muzdalfa mein namaz padhi aur eik iqaamat sey maghrib aur Isha ki dono namazein eik sath mila kar padhein aur kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko us jagah par aisey hi kartey dekha hai padhi. .
888,"ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey usi key misl riwayat kartey hain. Muhammad bin Bashaar ney ( « حدثنا » key bajaey ( « qaal Yahya » kaha hai. aur sahih Sufiyan wali riwayat hai, Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees jisey Sufiyan ney riwayat ki hai Ismail bin abi Khalid ki riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, aur Sufiyan ki hadees sahih Hasan hai, 2- Israel ney ye hadees abu-Is-haaq Sabeei sey riwayat ki hai aur abu-Is-haaq Sabeei ney Malik key dono beton Abdullah aur Khalid sey aur Abdullah aur Khalid ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai. aur Saeed bin Juber ki hadees jisey unhoney ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat ki hai Hasan sahih hai, Salma bin kuheil ney isey Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat ki hai, rahey abu-Is-haaq Sabeei to unhoney usey Malik key dono beton Abdullah aur Khalid sey aur un dono ney ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai, 3- is bab mein Ali , abu-Ayyub , Abdullah bin Saeed , Jabir aur Usama bin Zaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. isliye ke maghrib Muzdalfa aaney sey pehley nahin padhi jaeygi, jab hujjaaj jamaa  yani Muzdalfa jaeyn to dono namazein eik iqaamat sey ikhatti padhein aur unkey darmiyan koi nafl namaz nahin padheingey . yehi maslak hai jisey baaz ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kya hai aur uski taraf gaey hain aur yehi Sufiyan Sory ka bhi qol hai. unka kehna hai ke agar wo chahey to maghrib padhey phir Sham ka khana khaye , aur apney kapdey utarey phir takbir kahey aur Isha padhey , 5- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke maghrib aur Isha ko Muzdalfa main eik Azan aur do iqaamat key sath jama kerey. maghrib key liye Azan kahey aur takbir kahey aur maghrib padhey , phir takbir kahey aur Isha padhey ye Shafai ka qol hai."
889,"Najad key kuch log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye , us waqt aap Arfa mein they. unhoney aap sey Haj key mutalliq puchha to aap ney manadi ko hukm diya to usney aelan kiya : Haj Arafat mein theherna hai padhi. jo koi Muzdalfa ki raat ko tulu Fajr sey pehley Arfa aa jaey, usney Haj ko paa liya Meena key teen din hain, jo jaldi karey aur do din hi mein chala jaey to is par koi gunah nahin aur jo der karey teesrey din jaey to is par bhi koi gunah nahin. (Yahya ki riwayat mein itna izafa hai ke) aap ney eik shakhs ko peechhey bithaya aur usney aawaz lagai."
890,"Ibne-Abi umr ney basanad : (سفيان الثوري an بكير بن عطاء an عبدالرحمٰن بن يعمر an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم)  isi tarah usi maana ki hadees riwayat ki hai. ibne-Abi umr kehtey hain : (قال سفيان بن عيينة)‏‏‏‏ aur ye sab sey achchhi hadees hai jisey Sufiyan Sory ney riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Shoba ney bhi Buker bin Ata sey Sauri hi ki tarah riwayat ki hai. 2- Wakee ney is hadees ka zikr kiya to kaha ke ye hadees Haj key silsiley mein ''Ummul Manasik'' ki haisiyat rakhti hai. 3- Sahaba kiram mein sey ehle-ilm ka amal Abdur-Rehman bin Yamar ki hadees par hai ke ''jo tulu Fajr sey pehley Arafat mein nahin thehra , uska Haj faut ho gaya, aur agar wo tulu Fajr ke baad aaye to ye usey kafi nahin hoga. isey Umra bana ley aur agley saal Haj karey.''  ye Sauri , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai."
891,"Main Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas Muzdalfa aaya , jis waqt aap namaz key liye nikley to mainey aap sey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! main qabila Tai key dono pahadon sey hota huwa aaya hun, mainey apni sawari ko aur khud apney ko khub thakaa diya hai, Allah ki qism ! mainey koi pahad nahin chhoda jahan mainey (ye soch kar ke Arafat ka teela hai) wuqoof na kiya ho to kya mera Haj ho gaya? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo bhi hamari is namaz mein hazir raha aur usne hamarey sath qiyam kiya yahan tak ke hum yahan sey rawana hon aur wo is sey pehley din ya raat mein Arfa mein wuqoof kar chuka ho padhi. to usney apna Haj pura kar liya, aur apna mail kuchail khatam kar liya.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - « تَفَثَهُ » key maana « نسكه » key hain yani manaasik Haj key hain. aur iskey qol : (ما تركت من حبل إلا وقفت عليه) ''koi teela aisa na tha jahan mainey wuqoof na kiya ho.'' key silsiley mein ye hai ke jab ret ka teela ho to usey hubul aur jab pathar ka ho to usey Jabal kehtey hain."
892,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Muzdalfa sey raat hi mein asbab (kamzor aurton aur unkey asbab) key sath rawana kar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) , Umme-Habiba , Asma binte Abi Bakr aur Fazal bin Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
893,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney ghar walon mein sey kamzoron (yani aurton aur bachchon) ko pehley hi rawana kar diya, aur aap ney (un sey) farmaya : ''jab tak suraj na nikal jaey rami jimar na karna.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ( بعثني رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم في ثقل) sahih hadees hai, ye un sey kaee sanadon sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, Shoba ney ye hadees Mashash sey aur Mashash ney Ata sey aur ata ney ibne-Abbas sey aur ibne-Abbas ney Fazal bin Abbas sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney ghar walon mein sey kamzor logon ko pehley hi raat key waqt Muzdalfa sey Mina key liye rawana kar diya tha, ye hadees ghalat hai. Mashash ney is mein ghalati ki hai, unhoney is mein ''Fazal bin Abbas'' ka izafa kar diya hai. ibne-Jurej aur deegar logon ney ye hadees Ata sey aur Ata ney ibne-Abbas sey riwayat ki hai aur is mein Fazal bin Abbas key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. 3- Mashash Basra key rehney waley hain aur un sey Shoba ney riwayat ki hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai, wo is mein koi harj nahin samajhtey ke kamzor log Muzdalfa sey raat hi ko Mina key liye rawana ho jaeyn. 5- aksar ehle-ilm ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees key mutabiq hi kaha hai ke log jab tak suraj tulu na ho rami na karen. 6- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney raat hi ko rami kar leney ki rukhsat (chhoot) di hai. aur amal Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees par hai ke wo rami na karen jab tak ke suraj na nikal jaey, yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka qol hai."
894,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam daswen zil-hijja ko (thandi) chaasht key waqt rami kartey they aur uskey baad zawal key baad kartey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai ke wo daswen zi-hijja key zawal key baad hi rami karey.
895,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (Muzdalfa sey) suraj nikalney sey pehley lotey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- jahiliyat key zamaney mein log intizar kartey yahan tak ke suraj nikal aata phir laut'tey they."
896,"Hum log Muzdalfa mein thehrey huye they, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mushrekin jab tak ke suraj nikal nahin aata nahin laut'tey they aur kehtey they : Sabeer ! to roshan ho ja (tab hum lotengey), to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un ki mukhalifat ki, chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) suraj nikalney sey pehley lotey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
897,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap aisi kankariyon sey rami-jimar kar rahey they jo angoothey aur shahadat wali ungli key darmiyan pakdi ja sakti thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Amr bin ahwas (jo apni maa Umme Jundub Azdiya sey riwayat kartey hain), ibne-Abbas , Fazal bin Abbas , Abdur-Rehman bin Usman Tameemi aur Abdur-Rehman bin Muaz (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur isi ko ehle-ilm ney ikhtiyar kiya hai ke kankariyaan jin sey rami ki jati hai aisi hon jo angoothey aur shahadat ki ungli sey pakdi ja sake."
898,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam rami jimar us waqt kartey jab suraj dhal jata. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai.
899,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney daswen zil-hijj ko jamara ki rami sawari par ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Qudaama bin Abdullah , aur Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Amr bin Ahwas ki maa (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- baaz ney ye pasand kiya hai ke wo jamaraat tak pedal chal kar jaeyn. 5- ibne-Umar sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai ke aap jamaraat tak pedal chal kar jatey. 6- hamarey nazdik is hadees ki tauzih ye hai ke aap ney kabhi kabhar sawari par rami isliye ki taake aap key is kaam ki bhi log perwi karen. aur dono hi hadeeson par ehle-ilm ka amal hai."
900,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab rami jimar kartey, to jamaraat tak pedal aatey jatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz logon ney isey Ubedullah (Umree) sey riwayat kiya hai, lekin unhoney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- baaz log kehtey hain ke daswen zil-hijj ko sawar ho sakta hai, aur daswen key baad baqi dino mein pedal jaeyga. goya jisney ye kaha hai uskey paishe-nazar sirf Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key is kaam ki ittiba hai. isliye ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey ye bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke aap daswen zil-hijj ko sawar huye jab aap rami jimar karney gaey. aur daswen zil-hijj ko sirf jamara Aqba hi ki rami karey."
901,"jab Abdullah (Abdullah bin Masood) Jamara Aqba key paas aaye to wadi key bich mein khadey huye aur qibla rukh ho kar apney dahiney key muqabil rami shuru ki. phir saat kankariyon sey rami ki. har kankari par wo ''Allahu-Akbar'' kehtey they, phir unhoney kaha : Allah ki qism jis key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, us zaat ney bhi yahin sey rami ki jis par Sura Baqra nazil ki gaee hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Fazal bin Abbas , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, unkey nazdik pasandida yehi hai ke aadmi batan wadi mein khadey ho kar saat kankariyon sey rami karey aur har kankari par ''Allahu-Akbar'' kahey. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney ijazat di hai ke agar batan wadi sey rami karna mumkin na ho to aisi jagah sey karey jahan sey wo is par qadir ho maano wo batan wadi mein na ho."
902,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jamaraat ki rami aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee Allah key zikr ko qaaim karney key liye shuru ki gaee hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
903,"Mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha aap eik oontni par jamaraat ki rami kar rahey they, na logon ko dhakelne aur haankney ki aawaz thi aur na hato hato ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Qudaama bin Abdullah ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees isi tareeq sey jaani jati hai, ye Aiman bin Naabil ki hadees hai. aur Aiman ehale hadees (muhaddeseen) key nazdik harosemand hain. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Hanzala (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
904,"Hudaibia key saal hamney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath gaey aur oont ko saat saat aadmiyon ki janib sey nahar (zibeh) kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera , Aaisha aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke oont saat logon ki taraf sey aur gaaey saat logon ki taraf sey hogi. aur yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai aur Ahmed ka qol hai. 4- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kartey hain ke gaey saat logon ki taraf sey aur oont das logon ki taraf sey kafi hoga. ye Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. aur unhoney isi hadees sey daleel li hai. ibne-Abbas ki hadees ko hum sirf eik hi tareeq sey jantey hain. (dekhen aaney wali hadees : 905)"
905,"hum eik safar mein Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they ke eidul-Azha ka din aa gaya, chunanche gaaey mein hum saat saat log aur oont mein das das log shareek huye. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, aur ye Husain bin Waaqid ki hadees (riwayat) hai."
906,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zul-hulaifa mein (hadi key janwer ko) do jootiyon key haar pahnaaey aur un ki kohaan key daain taraf ashaar (cheer kar khoon nikal kar mal dena) kiya aur us sey khoon saaf kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo asha'aar (cheer kar khoon nikal kar mal dena) key qaail hain. yehi Sauri , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 3- Yusuf bin Esa kehtey hain ke mainey Wakee ko kehtey suna jis waqt unhoney ye hadees riwayat ki ke is silsiley mein ehale-raey key qol ko na dekho, kyonkey asha'aar (cheer kar khoon nikal kar mal dena) sunnat hai aur unka qol bidat hai. 4- mainey abu-Saaib ko kehtey suna ke hum log Wakee key paas they to unhoney apney paas key eik shakhs sey jo un logon mein sey tha jo raey mein ghor aur fikr kartey hain kaha ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney asha'aar (cheer kar khoon nikal kar mal dena) kya hai, aur Abu Haneefa kehtey hain ke wo musla hai to us aadmi ney kaha : Ibrahim Nakhai sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai unhoney bhi kaha hai ke asha'aar (cheer kar khoon nikal kar mal dena) musla hai, abu-Saaib kehtey hain : to mainey Wakee ko dekha ke (uski is baat sey) wo sakht naraz huye aur kaha : main tum sey kehta hun ke ''Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai'' aur tum kehtey ho : Ibrahim ney kaha : tum to is laaiq ho ke tumhen qaid kar diya jaey phir us waqt tak qaid sey tumhen na nikala jaey jab tak ke tum apney is qol sey baaz na aa jaao."
907,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apna hadi ka janwer qudaid sey kharida. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey Sauri ki hadees sey sirf Yahya bin Yamaan hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain : aur Nafey sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke ibne-Umar ney qudaid padhi. sey kharid , aur ye ziyada sahih hai."
908,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadi key qaladey baatey , phir aap na mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein) huye aur na hi aap ney koi kapda pehanna chhoda. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke jab aadmi hadi (key janwer) ko qaladey pehna dey aur wo Haj ka irada rakhta ho to is par kapda pehanna ya khushbu lagana haram nahin hota jab tak ke wo ehraam na baandh ley, 3- aur baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke jab aadmi apney hadi (key janwer) ko qulada pahna dey to uspar wo sab wajib ho jata hai jo eik mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein shakhs) par wajib hota hai."
909,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadi ki bakriyon key sarey qalaade main hi bat'ti thi padhi. phir aap ehraam na baandhtey (halal hi rehtey they). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghera mein sey baaz ehle-ilm key nazdik isi par amal hai, wo bakriyon ko qalade pahnaaney ke qaail hain."
910,"Mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! jo oont raastey mein marney lagen unhe main kya karun? aap ney farmaya : ''unhen nahar (zibeh) kar do, phir un ki jooti unhin ke khoon mein lat-pat kar do , phir unhen logon key liye chhod do ke wo unka gosht khaeyn.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Naajiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Zuweb Abu Qabisa Khuzai (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke nafli hadi ka janwer jab marney lagey to na wo khud usey khaye aur na uskey safar key sathi khaeyn. wo isey logon key liye chhod dey, ke wo isey khaeyn. yehi uskey liye kafi hai. ye Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. ye log kehtey hain ke agar usney is mein sey kuchh kha liya to jitna usney is mein sey khaya hai usi key b-qadr wo tawaan (jurmana) dey. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab wo nafli hadi key janwer mein sey kuchh kha ley to jisney khaya wo uska zaamin hoga."
911,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik shakhs ko hadii key oont haanktey dekha , to usey hukm diya ''is par sawar ho jaao.'' , usney arz kya : Allah key Rasool ! ye hadi ka oont hai, phir aap ney us sey teesri ya chauthi baar mein kaha : ''is par sawar ho jaao, tumhara bura ho padhi. ya tumhari halakat ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Abu-Hurera , aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sahaba kiram waghera mein sey ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney hadi key janwer par sawar honey ki ijazat di hai, jabke wo uska mohtaj ho, yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 4- baaz kehtey hain : jab tak majbur na ho hadi key janwer par sawar na ho."
912,"Jab Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jamara ki rami kar li to apney hadi key oont nahar (zibeh) kiye. phir sar moondney waley ko apney sar ka dahana janib (rukh)  diya aur usney sar mundaa, to ye baal aap ney abu-Talha ko diye , phir apna baayan janib usey diya to usney isey bhi mundaa to aap ney farmaya : ye baal logon mein taqseem kar do.''  ibne-Abi umr ki sanad sey Hisham sey isi tarah hadees riwayat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
913,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney sar mundwaya , Sahaba ki eik jamaat ney bhi sar mundwaya aur baaz logon ney baal katarwaaey. ibne-Umar kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik baar ya do baar farmaya : ''Allah sar mundwaney walon par reham farmaey.''  phir farmaya : ''katarwaney walon par bhi.''"
914,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke aurat apna sar mundwaey.
915,"Khilaas sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai, lekin is mein unhoney Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees mein iztirab (ikhtilaf) hai. ye hadees Hammad bin Salma sey b-tareeq : (Qatada an Aaysha Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney aurat ko apna sar mundwane sey mana farmaya. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo aurat key liye sar mundaaney ko durust nahin samajhtey unka khayal hai ke is par taqseer (baal katarwana) hai."
916,"Eik shakhs ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha ke mainey zibeh karney sey pehley sar mundaa liya? aap ney farmaya : ''ab zibeh kar lo koi harj nahin.'' eik doosrey ney puchha : mainey rami sey pehley nahar (zibeh) kar liya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''ab rami kar lo koi harj nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , ibne-Abbas , ibne-Umar , Usama bin Shareek (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : agar kisi nusuk ko yani rami ya nahar ya halaq waghera mein sey kisi eik ko doosrey sey pehley kar ley to is par dam (zabiha) lazim hoga (magar ye baat baghair daleel key hai)."
917,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aap key ehraam baandhney sey pehley aur daswin zil-hijja ko Baitullah ka tawaf karney sey pehley khushbu lagai jis mein mushk thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke mohrim (ehraam ki halat mein shakhs) jab daswin zil-hijja ko Jamara Aqba ki rami kar ley, janwer zibeh kar ley , aur sar mundaa ley ya baal katarwaa ley to ab uskey liye har wo chiz halal ho gaee jo is par haram thi siwaye aurton key. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 4- umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) sey marvi hai ke uskey liye har chiz halal ho gaee siwaye aurton aur khushbu key. 5- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain, aur yehi koofa walon ka bhi qol hai."
918,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey Muzdalfa sey Mina tak apna radeef banaya (yani aap mujhey apney peechhey sawari par bitha kar ley gaey) aap barabar talbiya kehtey rahey yahan tak ke aap ney Jamara (Aqba) ki rami ki. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , ibne-Masood , aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke Haaji talbiya band na karey jab tak ke Jamara ki rami na kar ley. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
919,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Umerey mein talbiya pukarna us waqt band kartey jab Hajare-Aswad ka istilaam kar letey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo kehtey hain ke Umra karney wala shakhs talbiya band na karey jab tak ke Hajare-Aswad ka istilaam na kar ley, 4- baaz kehtey hain ke jab Makkey key gharon yani Makka ki aabaadi mein pahunch jaey to talbiya pukarna band kar dey. lekin amal Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki (mazkoora) hadees par hai. yehi Sufiyan , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
920,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tawafe-ziyaarat ko raat tak muakhkhar (der karke) kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ney tawafe-ziyaarat ko raat tak muakhkhar karney ki ijazat di hai. aur baaz ney daswin zil-hijj ko tawafe-ziyaarat karney ko mustahab qarar diya hai, lekin baaz ney isey Mina key aakhiri din tak muakhkhar (der karke) karney ki gunjaaish rakhi hai."
921,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar , umr , aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) Abtah padhi. mein qiyam kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. hum isey sirf abdur-Razzaaq ki sanad sey jantey hain, wo Ubedullah bin umr sey riwayat kartey hain, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha , abu-Raafey aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney abtah mein qiyam ko mustahab qarar diya hai, wajib nahin, jo chahey wahan qiyam karey, 4- Shafai kehtey hain : abtah ka qiyam Haj key manaasik mein sey nahin hai. ye to bas eik maqam hai jahan Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qiyam farmaya."
922,"Wadi Mohsib mein qiyam koi chiz nahin padhi. , ye to bas eik jagah hai jahan Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qiyam farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- « تحصیب » key maana abtah mein qiyam karney key hain."
923,"Ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney abtah mein qiyam farmaya isliye ke yahan sey (Madiney key liye) rawana hona ziyada aasan tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. hum sey ibne-Abi umr ney bayan kiya, wo kehtey hain ke hum sey Sufiyan ney bayan kiya aur Sufiyan ney Hisham bin Urwa sey isi tarah ki hadees riwayat ki."
924,"Eik aurat ney apney bachchey ko Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki taraf utha kar puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya is par bhi Haj hai? aap ney farmaya : ''haan , aur ajr tujhey milega.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees gharib hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
925,"Jabir bin Abdullah Raziallahu anhuma ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye Muhammad bin Munkadir sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai. 3- ehle-ilm ka is par ijmaa' hai ke bachcha jab baligh honey sey pehley Haj kar ley to (uska fariza saaqit (khatm) nahin hoga) jab wo baligh ho jaeyga to uskey zimme Haj hoga, kam-sini ka ye Haj Islam key aaid karda fariza Haj key liye kafi nahin hoga. isi tarah ghulam ka maamla hai, agar wo ghulami mein Haj kar chuka ho phir azad kar diya jaey to azadi ki haalat mein is par Haj farz hoga jab wo uski sabeel (raasta) paa ley, ghulami ki haalat mein kiya huwa Haj kafi nahin hoga. Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi yehi qol hai."
926,"Merey baap ney Hajjatul-wadaa mein mujhey sath ley kar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kiya, main saat baras ka tha.  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
927,"Jab hamney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Haj kiya to hum aurton ki taraf sey talbiya kehtey aur bachchon ki taraf sey rami kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- ehle-ilm ka is baat par ittifaq hai ke aurat ki taraf sey koi doosra talbiya nahin kaheyga, balke wo khud hi talbiya kaheygi albatta uskey liye talbiya mein aawaz buland karna makrooh hai."
928,"Qabeela Khasam ki eik aurat ney arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey walid ko Allah key fariza Haj ney paa liya hai lekin wo itney boodhey hain ke oont ki peeth par beth nahin saktey (to kya kiya jaey?). aap ney farmaya : ''tu unki taraf sey Haj kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Fazal bin Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey Husain bin Auf Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 3- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke Sanan bin Abdullah Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ney apni phuphi sey aur un ki phuphi ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 4- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney baraahe-raast Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey bhi riwayat ki hai. 5- Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey in riwayaat key barey mein Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey puchha to unhoney kaha : is baab mein sab sey sahih riwayat wo hai jisey ibne-Abbas ney Fazal bin Abbas sey aur Fazal ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai. 6- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke iska bhi ehtimaal (gumaan) hai ke ibne-Abbas ney isey (apney bhai) Fazal sey aur unkey ilawa doosrey logon sey bhi suna ho aur un logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho, aur phir ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney isey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki ho aur jis sey unhoney isey suna ho uska naam zikr na kiya ho, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey is baab mein kaee aur bhi ahadees hain. 7- is bab mein Ali , Barida , Husain bin Auf , abu-Rizeen Aqeeli, Sauda binte Zamaa aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 8- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, aur yehi Sauri, ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain ke maiyat ki taraf sey Haj kiya ja sakta hai. 9- Malik kehtey hain : maiyat ki taraf sey Haj us waqt kiya jaeyga jab wo Haj karney ki wasiyat kar gaya ho. 10- baaz logon ney zinda shakhs ki taraf sey jab wo bahut ziyada boodha ho gaya ho ya aisi haalat mein ho ke wo Haj par qudrat na rakhta ho Haj karney ki ijazat di hai. yehi ibne-Mubarak aur Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
929,"eik aurat ney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : meri maa mar gaee hai, wo Haj nahin kar saki thi, kya main uski taraf sey Haj kar lun? aap ney farmaya : ''haan , to uski taraf sey Haj kar ley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees sahih hai."
930,"Unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! merey walid bahut boodhey hain, wo Haj aur Umra karney aur sawar ho kar safar karney ki taqat nahin rakhtay. (unke barey mein kya hukm hai?) aap ney farmaya : ''tum apney walid ki taraf sey Haj aur Umra kar lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Umerey ka zikr sirf isi hadees mein mazkur huwa hai ke aadmi ghair ki taraf sey Umra kar sakta hai."
931,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Umerey key barey mein puchha gaya : kya ye wajib hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin , lekin Umra karna behtar hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur yehi baaz ehle-ilm ka qol hai, wo kehtey hain ke Umra wajib nahin hai. 3- aur ye bhi kaha jata hai ke Haj do hain : eik Hajje-Akbar hai jo youme-nahar (daswin zil-Hijj ko) hota hai aur doosra Hajje-Asghar hai jisey Umra kehtey hain. 4- Shafai kehtey hain : Umerey (ka wajib hona) sunnat sey sabit hai, hum kisi aisey shakhs ko nahin jantey jisney isey chhodney ki ijazat di ho. aur iskey nafl honey key silsiley mein koi chiz sabit nahin hai. Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey jis sanad sey (nafl hona) marvi (riwayat hui) hai wo zaeef hai. us jaisi hadees sey hujjat nahin pakdi ja sakti , aur hum tak ye baat bhi pahunchi hai ke ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma isey wajib qarar detey they. ye sab Shafai ka kalam hai."
932,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Umrah Haj mein qiyamat tak key liye dakhil ho chuka hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein Suraqa bin Jaasham aur Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- is hadees ka maana ye hai ke Haj key mahinon mein Umra karney mein koi harj nahin. yehi tashreeh Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ney bhi ki hai ke jahiliyat key log haj key mahinon mein Umra nahin kartey they, jab Islam aaya to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney iski ijazat dey di aur farmaya : ''Umrah Haj mein qiyamat tak key liye dakhil ho chuka hai.''  yani Haj key mahinon mein Umra karney mein koi harj nahin hai, aur Ash'har Haj shawwaal, zi-qaada aur zil-hijj key das din hain.''  kisi shakhs key liye ye munasib nahin ke wo Haj key mahinon key ilawa kisi aur mahiney mein haj ka ehraam baandhey, aur hurmat waley mahiney ye hain : rajab, zi-qaada, zil-hijj aur muhrram. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm isi key qaail hain."
933,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik Umerey key baad doosra Umra darmiyan ke tamam gunah mita deta hai padhi. aur maqbool Haj ka badla jannat hi hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
934,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen hukm diya ke wo Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ko tan'eem padhi. sey Umra karaeyn. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
935,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Jaarana sey raat ko Umerey ki niyat sey nikley aur raat hi mein Makkey mein dakhil huye, aap ney apna Umra pura kiya, phir usi raat (Makka sey) nikal padey aur aap ney wapis Jaarana padhi. mein subah ki, goya aap ney wahin raat guzaari ho, aur jab doosrey din suraj dhal gaya to aap wadi sarf padhi. sey nikley yahan tak ke us raastey par aaye jis sey wadi sarf wala raasta aa kar mil jata hai. isi wajeh sey (bahut sey) logon sey aap ka Umra poshida raha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum is hadees key ilawa Muharrish Ka'bi ki koi aur hadees nahin jantey jisey unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki ho aur kaha jata hai : (جاء مع الطريق) wala tukda wusul hua hai."
936,"Ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey puchha gaya : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kis mahiney mein Umra kiya tha? to unhoney kaha : rajab mein , is par Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney jo bhi Umra kiya, is mein wo yani ibne-Umar aap key sath they, aap ney rajab key mahiney mein kabhi bhi Umra nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Habib bin abi Sabit ney Urwa bin Zuber sey nahin suna hai."
937,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney chaar Umerey kiye , un mein sey eik rajab mein tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai."
938,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney zi-qaada key mahina mein Umra kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
939,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Ramzan ka Umra eik Haj key barabar hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme Maaqil ki hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai. 2- (Wahab key bajaey) Harim bin khanbash bhi kaha jata hai. bayan aur Jabir ney yun kaha hai :(عن الشعبي an وهب بن خنبش) aur Dawud Awdi ney yun kaha hai : (عن الشعبي an هرم بن خنبش) lekin sahih Wahab bin Khanbash hi hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Jabir , Abu-Hurera , Anas aur Wahab bin Khanbash (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Sabit hai ke Ramzan ka Umra Haj key sawab barabar hai, Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain ke is hadees ka mafhoom bhi is hadees key mafhoom ki tarah hai jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki gaee hai ke jisney Sura « قل هو الله أحد » padhi usney tihai Quran padha."
940,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jis ka koi uzu (ang) toot jaey ya wo landaa ho jaey to uskey liye ehraam khol dena durust hai, is par doosra Haj lazim hoga.''  mainey iska zikr Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey kiya to un dono ney kaha ke unhoney (Hujjaaj) sach kaha. Is-haq bin Mansoor ki sanad bhi Hujjaaj (Raziallahu anhu) sey Isi key misl riwayat hai albatta is mein (عن الحجاج بن عمرو قال قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم) key bajaey (سمعت رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم ) key alfaz hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- isi tarah kaee aur logon ney bhi Hujjaaj sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. 3- Maamar aur Muawiya bin Salam ney bhi ye hadees ba-tareeq : (Yahya bin abi Kasir an Akrama an Abdullah bin Raafey an Hujjaj bin Amr an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, 4- aur Hujjaaj ney apni riwayat mein Abdullah bin Raafey ka zikr nahin kiya hai, Hujjaaj Al Sawwaf  muhaddeseen key nazdik bharosemand aur Hafiz hain. 5- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Maamar aur Muawiya bin Salam ki riwayat sab sey ziyada sahih hai. 6- Abdur-Razzaaq ney basanad (Maamar an Yahya bin abi Kasir an Akrama an Abdullah bin Raafey an Hujjaj bin Amr an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) isi tarah riwayat ki hai."
941,"Zaba'a binte Zuber ney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar kaha : Allah key Rasool ! main Haj ka irada rakhti hun, to kya main shart laga sakti hun? (ke agar koi uzr sharaee laahiq huwa to ehraam khol dungi) aap ney farmaya : ''haan, to unhoney puchha : main kaisey kahun? aap ney farmaya : (لبيك اللهم لبيك لبيك  من الأرض حيث تحبسني)''hazir hun aey Allah hazir hun hazir hun, merey ehraam kholney ki jagah wo hai jahan to mujhey rok dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Asma binte Abi Bakr aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- isi par baaz ehle-ilm ka amal hai, wo Haj mein shart laga leney ko durust samajhtey hain. wo kehtey hain ke agar usney shart kar li phir usey koi marz ya uzr laahiq huwa to uskey liye jayez hai ke wo halal ho jaey aur apney ehraam sey nikal aaye. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm Haj mein shart laganey key qaail nahin hain. wo kehtey hain ke agar usney shart laga bhi li to usey ehraam sey nikalney ka haq nahin, ye log isey us shakhs ki tarah samajhtey hain jisney shart nahin lagai hai."
942,wo Haj mein shart laganey sey inkar kartey they aur kehtey they : kya tumharey liye tumharey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka tariqa kafi nahin hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
943,"Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey zikr kiya ke Safiya bint Hayi Mina key dino mein haaiza ho gaee hain, aap ney puchha : ''kya wo hamein (Makkey sey rawana honey sey) rok deygi?'' logon ney arz kiya : wo tawafe-ifaaza kar chuki hain, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tab to koi harj nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke aurat jab tawafe ziyaarat kar chuki ho aur phir usey haiz aa jaey to wo rawana ho sakti hai, tawafe-wadaa' chhod deney sey is par koi chiz lazim nahin hogi. yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai."
944,"Jisney Baitullah ka Haj kiya, uska aakhiri kaam Baitullah ka tawaf (wadaa') hona chahiye haaiza aurton key siwa ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen rukhsat (chhoot) di hai.Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai."
945,Mujhey haiz aa gaya chunanche Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey tawaf key ilawa sabhi manaasik ada karney ka hukm diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is tareeq key ilawa sey bhi Aaisha sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi hadees par amal hai ke haaiza Khana-Kaaba key tawaf key ilawa sabhi manaasik ada kareygi.
946,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''jisney us ghar (Baitullah) ka Haj ya Umra kiya to chahiye ke uska aakhiri kaam (Baitullah) ka tawaf ho. to unsey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : tum apney haathon key bal zamin par giron yani halak ho, tum ney ye baat Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey suni aur hamein nahin batai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Haris bin Abdullah bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees gharib hai, isi tarah doosrey aur logon ney bhi Hujjaaj bin Irtaat sey isi key jiasi riwayat ki hai. aur is sanad key baaz hissey ke silsiley mein Hujjaaj sey ikhtilaf kiya gaya hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
947,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Haj aur Umra dono ko mila kar eik sath kiya aur unke liye eik hi tawaf kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo kehtey hain ke Hajje-Qiran karney wala eik hi tawaf kerega. yehi Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 4- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka kehna hai ke wo do tawaf aur do saee karega. yehi Sauri aur ehle-Koofa ka qol hai."
948,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney Haj aur Umerey dono ka ehraam baandha uskey liye eik tawaf aur eik saee kafi hai yahan tak ke wo un dono ka ehraam khol dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- isey in alfaz key sath riwayat karney mein Abdul-Azeez Daraawardi munfarid (alag) hain, isey doosrey kaee aur logon ney bhi Ubedullah bin Umar  sey riwayat kiya hai, lekin in logon ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai aur yehi ziyada sahih hai."
949,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Muhaajir apney Haj key manaasik ada karney ke baad Makkey mein teen din thehar sakta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur is sanad sey aur tarah sey bhi ye hadees marfooan riwayat ki gaee hai.
950,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab kisi ghazwey, Haj ya Umerey sey laut'tey aur kisi buland maqam par chadhtey to teen baar Allahu-Akbar kehtey, phir kehtey : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير آيبون تائبون عابدون سائحون لربنا حامدون صدق الله وعده ونصر عبده وهزم الأحزاب) ''Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin, wo akela hai, uska koi shareek nahin. saltanat usi ki hai aur tamam tareefen bhi usi key liye hain aur wo har chiz par qadir hai. hum lotney waley hain, ruju karney waley hain, ibadat karney waley hain, sair karney waley hain, apney rab ki tareef karney waley hain, Allah ney apna wada sach kar dikhaya, apney bandey ki madad ki, aur tanha hi sari faujon ko shikast dey di.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Bara , Anas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
951,"Hum log eik safar mein Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath they, aap ney dekha ke eik shakhs apney oont sey gir pada, uski gardan toot gaee aur wo mar gaya wo mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein shakhs) tha, to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''isey pani aur beeri key patton sey ghusl do aur isey uskey inhi (ehraam ke) dono kapdon mein kafnaao aur uska sar na chhupaao, isliye ke wo qiyamat key din talbiya pukarta huwa uthaya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. yehi Sufiyan Sory , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke jab mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein shakhs) mar jata hai to uska ehraam khatam ho jata hai, aur uskey sath bhi wohi sab kuchh kiya jaeyga jo ghair mohrim key sath kiya jata hai."
952,"umr bin Ubedullah bin Maamar ki aankhen dukhney lagin, wo ehraam sey they, unhoney Aban bin Usman sey masla poochha, to unhoney kaha : un mein eilwey ka lep kar lo, kyonkey mainey Usman bin Affaan (Raziallahu anhu) ko iska zikr kartey suna hai, wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kar rahey they aap ney farmaya : ''in par eilwey ka lep kar lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, ye log mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein shakhs) ke aisi dawaa sey ilaj karney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey jis mein khushbu na ho."
953,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Makka mein dakhil honey sey pehley unkey paas sey guzrey , wo hudaibiya mein they, ehraam baandhey huye they. aur eik haandi key nichey aag jala rahey they. juein unkey munh par gir rahi thin to aap ney puchha : kya ye juein tumhen takleef pahuncha rahi hain? kaha : haan , aap ney farmaya : ''sar mundwaa lo aur chhe miskinon ko eik farq khana khila do, (farq teen saa ka hota hai) ya teen din key rozey rakh lo. ya eik janwer qurban kar do. ibne-Abi Najeeh ki riwayat mein hai.'' ya eik bakri zibeh kar do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram (Raziallauh anhum) waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ke mohrim (ehraam ki haalat mein shakhs) jab apna sar munda ley, ya aisey kapdey pehan ley jinka pehanna ehraam mein durust nahin ya khushbu laga ley. to is par usi key jaisa kaffara hoga jo Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
954,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney charwaahon ko rukhsat (chhoot) di ke eik din rami karen aur eik din chhod den. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- isi tarah ibne Uena ney bhi riwayat ki hai, aur Malik bin Anas ney basanad (Abdullah bin abi Bakar bin Muhammad ibne Amr bin Hazam an Abeeh an abi Al Badah bin Aasim bin Adi an Abeeh an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai, aur Malik ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney charwaahon ko rukhsat di hai ke wo eik din rami karen aur eik din tarak kar den."
955,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney oont key charwaahon ko (Meena mein) raat guzarney key silsiley mein rukhsat (chhoot) di ke wo daswin zil-hijj ko (Jamara Aqba ki) rami kar lein. phir daswin zil-hijj key baad key do dino ki rami jama kar ke eik din mein ikhatti kar lein padhi. (Malik kehtey hain : mera guman hai ke Raavi ney kaha). ''pehley din rami kar ley phir kooch key din rami karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, aur ye ibne Uena ki Abdullah bin Abi Bakr sey riwayat wali hadees sey ziyada sahih hai."
956,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas Yamen sey aaye to aap ney puchha : ''tum ney kya talbiya pukara, aur kon sa ehraam baandha hai?'' unhoney arz kiya : mainey wohi talbiya pukara , aur isi ka ehraam baandha hai jiska talbiya Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney pukara, aur jo ehraam Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney baandha hai.  aap ney farmaya : ''agar merey sath hadi key janwer na hotey to main ehraam khol deta.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
957,mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey puchha : Haje-Akbar ( badey haj (ka din kon sa hai? to aap ney farmaya : « youmun-Nahar» '' qurbani ka din ''.
958,"Haje-Akbar (badey Haj) ka din daswin zii-hijja ka din hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ibne-Abi umr ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai aur ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai aur ibne Uena ki maqoof riwayat Muhammad bin Is-haq ki marfoo riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai. isi tarah bahut sey haafizee-hadees ney isey basanad (Abi Ishaaq an al-Haaris an Ali) moqufan riwayat kiya hai, Shoba ney bhi Abu-Is'haq Sabeei sey riwayat ki hai unhoney yun kaha hai (an Abdullah bin Murra an al-Haaris an Ali mauqufan)."
959,"Ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma Hajare-Aswad aur rukn Yamaani par aisi bheed lagatey they jo mainey Sahaba mein sey kisi ko kartey nahin dekha. to mainey puchha : abu-Abdur-Rehman ! aap dono rukn par aisi bheed lagatey hain ke mainey Sahaba mein sey kisi ko aisa kartey nahin dekha? to unhoney kaha : agar main aisa karta hun to isliye ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''in par haath pherna gunahon ka kaffara hai.'' aur mainey aap ko farmatey suna hai : ''jisney is ghar ka tawaf saat martaba (saat chakkar) kiya aur usey gina, to ye aisey hi hai goya usney eik ghulam azad kiya.'' aur mainey aap ko farmatey suna hai : ''wo jitney bhi qadam rakhey aur uthaeyga Allah har eik key badley uski eik ghalati maaf karega aur eik neki likheyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Hammad bin Zaid ney ba-tareeq : (Ata bin Sayib, an ibne Ubaid bin Umair, an ibne-Umar) riwayat ki hai aur is mein unhoney ibne Ubaid key baap key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai."
960,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Baitullah key gird tawaf namaz key tarah hai. albatta is main tum bol saktey ho (jab ke namaz main tum bol nahin saktey) to jo is mein boley wo zaban sey bhali baat hi nikaley.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees ibne Taaus waghera ney ibne-Abbas sey moqufan riwayat ki hai. hum isey sirf Ata bin Saaib ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain. 2- isi par aksar ehle-ilm ka amal hai, ye log is baat ko mustahab qarar detey hain ke aadmi tawaf mein bila zarurat na boley (aur agar boley) to Allah ka zikr karey ya phir ilm ki koi baat kahey."
961,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hajare-Aswad key barey mein farmaya : ''Allah ki qism ! Allah isey qiyamat key din is haal mein uthaeyga ke iski do aankhen hongi, jis sey ye dekheyga, eik zaban hogi jis sey ye boleyga۔ aur ye us shakhs key eman ki gawahi dega jisney haq key sath (yani eman aur ajr ki niyat sey) uska istilaam kiya hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
962,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam haalate ehraam mein zaitun ka tel lagatey they aur ye (tel) baghair khushbu key hota tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, isey hum sirf Farqad Sabkhi ki riwayat sey jantey hain, aur Farqad ney Saeed bin Juber sey riwayat ki hai. Yahya bin Saeed ney Farqad Sabkhi key silsiley mein kalam kya hai, aur Farqad sey logon ney riwayat ki hai. 2muqattat key maana khushbudar ke hain."
963,"Wo zamzam ka pani sath Madina ley jati thin, aur bayan karti thin ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bhi zamzam sath ley jatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain."
964,"Mainey Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : mujh sey aap koi aisi baat bayan kijiye jo aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey yad kar rakhi ho. bataiye aap ney aathwein zil-hijj ko Zohar kahan padhi? unhoney kaha : Mina mein , (phir) mainey puchha : aur kooch key din Asr kahan padhi? kaha : abtah mein lekin tum wesey hi karo jaisey tumharey Ameer aur hukkaam kartey hain. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur Is-haq bin Yusuf Al Azraq ki riwayat sey gharib jaani jati hai jisey unhoney Sauri sey riwayat ki hai."
